onverted to SpaceX equity upon the xAI Merger\n\n---\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThe filing **acknowledges but does not itemize** intercompany transactions between SpaceX, xAI, and X Holdings. The statement that "all historical related party transactions between the entities have been eliminated in consolidation" is the only direct reference. All specifically quantified related party transactions in the provided text are with **external affiliated entities**—primarily Tesla, The Boring Company, Musk Industries LLC, a Musk-owned security company, and Valor Equity Partners. The absence of detailed intercompany transaction disclosure may reflect that these were eliminated in consolidation and therefore not required to be separately itemized, or that such details appear in portions of the S-1 not included in the provided chunks.',
